## End-of-session workflow
The generic branch → PR → CI-green → squash-merge sequence is your global
`~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` checklist (its `gh run watch` step waits for GitHub checks
name-agnostically); keep only Hoard's deltas here, e.g.:
- Deploy: `./scripts/deploy.sh` (the `deploy` skill drives it) after main CI is green.
- Migrations run on container boot (`scripts/start.mjs`) — never pre-apply on prod.
- Docs to update in the same PR: `MEMORY.md` / `CLAUDE.md` / `plans/README.md`.
